      • nonValidatingBuilder

        public static BdplQuery.Builder nonValidatingBuilder()
        This builder can be made to build a BdplQuery without checking consistency. This means that there is no checking whether all setters were invoked (with not null values) before building. Useful e.g. in UnitTests where inconsistent BdplQuery are acceptable.
        Parameters:
        validating - whether to check all setters were called (with not null values) before building
